The best part- you will earn reward points for doing the same things you’ve always had to do... only now you can do them from the comfort of your couch and whenever works best for you. Modento is here to make dentistry as painless as possible.

NOTE: You will be able sign up and use this application only if your dental practice is using Modento platform. Ask your dentist if you are not sure.
